Titolo: Yo-kai Watch Jam: Yo-kai Academy Y – Waiwai Gakuen Seikatsu

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Yo-kai Watch Jam: Yo-kai Academy Y – Waiwai Gakuen Seikatsu is a 2020 role-playing game developed and published by Level-5 for the Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4. A spin-off installment in the Yo-kai Watch series, Yo-kai Watch Jam sees the player as Jinpei Jiba, a student at the fictitious Y Academy, who investigates mysteries occurring in the academy and surrounding areas.Yo-kai Watch Jam was received positively by critics, who praised the game's combat system and environment and school life mode, due to its routine feeling and open world-like style.